WEBVTT

00:18.920 --> 00:20.360
The Li-Wei feud has unsettled the court.

00:21.520 --> 00:24.040
If you now intend to stand apart
and form your own power,

00:25.440 --> 00:28.480
would that not throw the situation
into deeper chaos?

00:41.120 --> 00:42.120
A man

00:43.240 --> 00:45.240
does not scale another's wall.

00:46.280 --> 00:47.560
A minister

00:48.600 --> 00:50.480
does not bend with shifting winds.

00:52.600 --> 00:54.080
That is all I will say.

00:55.640 --> 00:58.200
Zheng! Zheng!

00:58.280 --> 00:59.520
Are you in there?

01:00.800 --> 01:04.680
Zheng, Mrs. Zhao says
to come home for lunch.

01:11.240 --> 01:13.400
Little miss, why not step inside
and sit a while?

01:14.760 --> 01:17.840
I would never step into a villain's house.

01:17.920 --> 01:19.360
Thank you, Scholar Sir.

01:19.960 --> 01:21.440
Why do you call me Scholar Sir?

01:22.040 --> 01:25.440
My sister said
your carriage is filled with books.

01:28.320 --> 01:29.920
I shall not disturb you further.

01:31.520 --> 01:33.640
Pretend I was never here.

01:39.760 --> 01:40.600
Let's go.

02:25.840 --> 02:28.400
So, he truly is Marquis Wu'an?

02:35.480 --> 02:36.920
He only crushed a teacup.

02:37.920 --> 02:39.760
Is that all the legendary Marquis
amounts to?

02:45.680 --> 02:48.440
His internal force
is far stronger than before.

04:18.200 --> 04:21.920
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

04:31.480 --> 04:32.640
FAN'S BRAISED MEAT

04:43.000 --> 04:43.840
Changyu.

04:45.240 --> 04:46.080
Qian.

04:46.160 --> 04:49.640
Covered in blood and grease all day,
and somehow you're still glowing.

04:50.640 --> 04:52.160
Get in. I'll take you home.

04:53.000 --> 04:54.640
It's fine. I can walk back.

04:54.720 --> 04:56.280
Normally, I would let you,

04:56.360 --> 04:59.040
but tonight, there were
too many banquet orders. I kept you late.

04:59.120 --> 05:01.800
It's dark. I won't be at ease
letting you walk alone.

05:03.280 --> 05:04.120
Get in.

05:05.720 --> 05:07.560
I can handle the rest. You go on ahead.

05:08.160 --> 05:09.560
All right. I appreciate it.

05:36.200 --> 05:37.040
Come out.

05:40.320 --> 05:43.040
-Marquis.
-Marquis, forgive us. We arrived late.

05:43.120 --> 05:43.960
BLOODCLAD CAVALRY GUARD XIE WU
BLOODCLAD CAVALRY GUARD XIE QI

05:47.720 --> 05:48.560
Rise.

05:51.120 --> 05:52.240
How many of you came?

05:53.200 --> 05:54.520
Only Xie Qi and I.

05:54.600 --> 05:56.880
We feared being followed.
We brought no other guards.

05:56.960 --> 05:58.600
Marquis, thank heaven you are unharmed.

06:00.880 --> 06:02.400
Xie Yi and Xie San

06:03.600 --> 06:04.760
died because of me.

06:07.960 --> 06:09.160
We brothers swore an oath.

06:09.240 --> 06:11.880
To protect you with our lives.
Even death we would accept.

06:14.240 --> 06:15.240
No man of the Xie clan

06:16.240 --> 06:17.960
will fall without reckoning.

06:18.040 --> 06:20.560
The brothers in camp await your return.

06:20.640 --> 06:23.440
Wei Xuan is running rampant.

06:24.400 --> 06:26.600
He struts through the ranks
daily like a peacock.

06:27.200 --> 06:29.640
The men can hardly stop themselves
from feeding him to the wolves.

06:29.720 --> 06:30.880
Let him preen.

06:33.160 --> 06:34.400
Soon enough,

06:34.480 --> 06:37.560
a bloody clash with Prince Changxin
at Chongzhou cannot be avoided.

06:37.640 --> 06:39.800
For now, securing grain stores
is paramount.

06:39.880 --> 06:41.760
The court refuses to release provisions.

06:41.840 --> 06:43.600
Wei Xuan, obeying
Chancellor Wei's command,

06:43.680 --> 06:44.800
plans to levy grain locally.

06:51.480 --> 06:52.480
Sixteen years ago,

06:53.240 --> 06:54.920
the Xie army suffered defeat at Jinzhou

06:55.680 --> 06:57.840
because supply lines failed.

07:01.120 --> 07:02.800
I will not repeat that mistake.

07:05.640 --> 07:07.600
Wei Xuan is hungry for glory.

07:07.680 --> 07:09.640
If he falls to Changxin,
it will not surprise me.

07:10.440 --> 07:11.840
We may even turn that to advantage.

07:11.920 --> 07:14.640
Let him lead his incompetent men as bait.

07:15.480 --> 07:17.280
Draw Changxin south.

07:17.360 --> 07:20.080
When the moment comes,
I have my own strategy.

07:20.680 --> 07:22.920
So you will not return to camp yet?

07:25.520 --> 07:26.880
You return first.

07:26.960 --> 07:28.600
Spread word of my death.

07:28.680 --> 07:29.960
The wider it spreads, the better.

07:30.720 --> 07:31.560
Understood.

07:39.280 --> 07:40.720
-Go.
-Yes.

07:49.360 --> 07:50.920
All the braised pork sold out today.

07:51.000 --> 07:53.520
-The pig's head was especially popular.
-Really?

07:54.600 --> 07:56.800
Mrs. Wang said
her daughter is getting married.

07:57.680 --> 07:59.040
She ordered half a pig from me.

07:59.120 --> 08:01.280
That means more work for you.

08:01.360 --> 08:03.480
Work like that, I welcome.

08:08.400 --> 08:10.080
Who… Who are you?

08:13.960 --> 08:14.920
I'll go check.

08:29.960 --> 08:31.640
Qian, stay inside.

08:32.520 --> 08:33.480
I can handle this.

08:34.000 --> 08:34.880
Take her down.

08:46.840 --> 08:49.200
Who sent you? Was it him?

08:49.280 --> 08:51.160
After all these years,
why won't he leave me alone?

08:55.520 --> 08:56.360
What are you doing?

08:56.440 --> 08:59.280
Help. Someone help!

09:11.920 --> 09:12.920
Changyu, watch out!

09:19.720 --> 09:21.560
You can't just leave me!

09:21.640 --> 09:23.400
That voice sounds familiar.

09:27.040 --> 09:29.280
-Guo Dali.
-Guo Dali?

09:30.200 --> 09:31.200
Mrs. Fan.

09:31.280 --> 09:32.840
Heroine Fan.

09:32.920 --> 09:34.320
Your Ladyship!

09:34.400 --> 09:35.720
I just made a foolish mistake!

09:35.800 --> 09:37.600
You have crossed me again and again.

09:37.680 --> 09:39.160
Hardly a one-time mistake.

09:39.240 --> 09:40.960
Someone paid us.

09:41.040 --> 09:42.280
They hired us to kill you.

09:44.200 --> 09:45.560
-Who?
-Who?

09:45.640 --> 09:46.600
Who…

09:48.440 --> 09:49.560
Who!

09:50.160 --> 09:51.360
Changyu!

09:54.400 --> 09:56.920
Might as well sell you both.

10:04.640 --> 10:05.320
Go to hell!

10:06.280 --> 10:09.160
Bastard. If you dare, face me!

10:10.520 --> 10:12.240
Fine! You're going to get it.

10:12.320 --> 10:13.240
Changyu!

10:14.520 --> 10:15.360
I will…

10:24.360 --> 10:26.400
Changyu. Changyu.

10:29.880 --> 10:30.920
Are you hurt?

10:42.840 --> 10:44.680
XIGU ALLEY

10:46.120 --> 10:48.360
Yan Zheng, did you run into Changyu?

10:49.400 --> 10:50.400
What happened?

10:50.480 --> 10:52.640
-She was drugged. Bring cold water.
-All right.

10:52.720 --> 10:54.080
Zhao, hurry. Help me.

10:54.800 --> 10:55.920
Hello, sir.

11:09.440 --> 11:11.040
What in the world is this?

11:13.160 --> 11:14.080
What?

11:14.160 --> 11:15.960
My backside. It hurts.

11:16.040 --> 11:16.880
Hurts?

11:16.960 --> 11:18.680
-Where does it hurt?
-My backside.

11:18.760 --> 11:19.760
Your backside what?

11:19.840 --> 11:21.120
It hurts.

11:21.200 --> 11:23.200
Good. I wish it hurt worse.

11:35.360 --> 11:36.760
You worthless scum!

11:39.520 --> 11:40.360
Spare me.

11:40.440 --> 11:41.760
Please spare me.

11:41.840 --> 11:43.760
I'm not a Qingfeng Stronghold bandit.

11:43.840 --> 11:46.560
At Yixiang Restaurant, those women…

11:47.680 --> 11:50.000
No, those two ladies humiliated me.

11:50.080 --> 11:52.560
I only meant to scare them a little.

11:55.480 --> 11:56.480
Guo Dali!

11:56.560 --> 11:58.480
You had your grudges with Fan Erniu.

11:58.560 --> 12:00.600
And now you take it out
on his poor daughter?

12:00.680 --> 12:02.520
-Have you no shame?
-My backside…

12:02.600 --> 12:04.120
Enough.

12:04.200 --> 12:05.800
Must you keep shouting?

12:06.400 --> 12:08.240
Do you want the whole roof torn down?

12:09.720 --> 12:11.520
It hurts! It hurts!

12:18.040 --> 12:19.000
Scare them?

12:20.080 --> 12:21.760
You drugged her!

12:22.760 --> 12:24.240
What exactly were you planning?

12:25.800 --> 12:27.960
I was going to knock them
unconscious first…

12:32.160 --> 12:33.520
And then?

12:38.240 --> 12:39.360
Speak!

12:40.440 --> 12:42.520
Break her meridians…

12:46.200 --> 12:47.160
And then?

12:53.320 --> 12:55.320
Sell her into the mountains…

13:07.680 --> 13:08.520
Stop!

13:09.680 --> 13:12.080
Yan, enough. There is no need
to stain your hands further.

13:13.040 --> 13:14.240
His punishment will be decided

13:14.320 --> 13:15.920
-by the authorities.
-Authorities?

13:16.600 --> 13:18.400
If I had not been there tonight,

13:18.480 --> 13:19.960
Changyu would already be dead!

13:20.760 --> 13:23.840
You have confessed.
No one could save you now!

13:25.440 --> 13:28.280
My enemy is mine to deal with!

13:30.680 --> 13:31.520
-Stop.
-I beg you!

13:31.600 --> 13:32.400
Yan Zheng.

13:38.240 --> 13:40.800
Do not kill him. He isn't worth it.

13:57.040 --> 13:57.880
Are you hurt?

13:59.160 --> 14:00.000
Lie back down.

14:04.200 --> 14:06.840
Go back to sleep. I will not kill anyone.

14:17.680 --> 14:19.880
All right, no more tears.

14:21.200 --> 14:22.960
I'm stronger than an ox.

14:23.040 --> 14:23.880
See?

14:24.520 --> 14:26.600
Hands fine. Feet fine.

14:27.200 --> 14:28.040
Stop crying.

14:33.880 --> 14:35.080
Changyu…

14:39.440 --> 14:41.360
Will you fetch me a basin of hot water?

14:42.960 --> 14:43.840
All right.

14:58.840 --> 15:01.400
How is your head? Does it still ache?

15:02.760 --> 15:05.520
Anywhere else uncomfortable?

15:07.480 --> 15:09.120
If you had killed someone for me

15:10.080 --> 15:11.520
and ended up in prison,

15:13.200 --> 15:14.280
that would hurt far worse.

15:31.240 --> 15:32.160
Promise me.

15:33.480 --> 15:34.440
Do not risk yourself.

15:41.080 --> 15:42.040
Do not worry.

15:43.960 --> 15:45.200
I won't.

15:59.400 --> 16:02.280
Ms. Yu, all doors and windows are secured.

16:03.040 --> 16:04.960
The fire buckets are filled.

16:06.080 --> 16:09.120
The men are rotating watch every hour.

16:09.720 --> 16:11.240
Anything else?

16:13.240 --> 16:17.240
Ms. Yu, is war coming?

16:19.720 --> 16:23.200
Tomorrow, add two more locks.

16:23.280 --> 16:25.600
There are already double doors
and three locks.

16:25.680 --> 16:27.800
You want more?

16:27.880 --> 16:30.240
Yes. Add another.

16:30.880 --> 16:33.760
And reinforce the door frames with iron.

16:35.040 --> 16:36.040
Understood.

17:53.880 --> 17:56.520
-Mother.
-Have you been good today?

17:56.600 --> 17:59.280
Very good. I didn't go outside.

17:59.880 --> 18:03.160
I finished all the homework you left.

18:04.600 --> 18:05.840
Such a good child.

18:06.680 --> 18:09.400
Then tomorrow,
we must be just as good, all right?

18:20.600 --> 18:22.720
LUYUAN

18:50.160 --> 18:51.360
Excellent move. Such--

18:54.680 --> 18:56.720
I didn't expect you to play Go, An Xu.

18:57.520 --> 18:58.360
I know a little.

19:00.120 --> 19:02.200
Then indulge me in a match.

19:02.280 --> 19:03.160
Of course!

19:05.200 --> 19:06.040
Gladly.

19:16.960 --> 19:17.840
That was satisfying.

19:18.560 --> 19:20.400
We must play again tomorrow.

19:21.000 --> 19:22.080
I would like that.

19:23.680 --> 19:24.560
Headmaster.

19:29.200 --> 19:32.480
When I was young,
I once read part of a Go manual.

19:32.560 --> 19:33.720
Hidden Principles of Qi.

19:34.400 --> 19:36.880
I heard the Imperial Library
houses over 10,000 volumes.

19:36.960 --> 19:38.200
I searched for it,

19:38.720 --> 19:40.000
but never found it.

19:40.720 --> 19:43.960
That book is not in the Imperial Library.

19:45.440 --> 19:49.600
However, the Gongsun family collection
does hold a complete copy.

19:50.680 --> 19:53.840
It belonged to my grandfather.
It is not for lending.

19:59.320 --> 20:00.720
A gentleman does not covet
another's treasure.

20:00.800 --> 20:03.280
Anyone would treasure something this rare.

20:07.400 --> 20:08.760
Still,

20:10.560 --> 20:13.000
though it cannot be lent,

20:13.800 --> 20:17.040
I could transcribe
the remaining pages for you.

20:18.600 --> 20:19.440
Thank you, Headmaster.

20:19.520 --> 20:26.400
WISDOM THROUGH STUDY

20:35.720 --> 20:39.040
A ruler must shoulder the duty
of protecting the common people.

21:00.040 --> 21:02.640
To Her Highness, Empress Dowager An.

21:02.720 --> 21:04.880
The newly admitted student An Xu

21:04.960 --> 21:07.480
is in truth the Grand Princess
in disguise.

21:07.560 --> 21:10.320
I have confirmed this
and dare not conceal it.

21:10.400 --> 21:12.720
I respectfully report this
for Your Highness's judgment.

21:14.200 --> 21:16.240
YIXIANG RESTAURANT

21:21.360 --> 21:22.200
Qian.

21:23.240 --> 21:24.400
Qian?

21:34.400 --> 21:35.240
Where is she?

21:53.000 --> 21:54.120
Changyu.

21:55.120 --> 21:56.640
You nearly scared the life out of me.

21:56.720 --> 21:58.720
You told me to come, then vanished.

21:58.800 --> 21:59.720
I was about to head out.

22:00.840 --> 22:01.800
Come, sit.

22:10.920 --> 22:12.000
Are you feeling better now?

22:12.080 --> 22:13.720
Much better.

22:13.800 --> 22:16.600
You kept sending medicine and food.
I've practically grown plump.

22:18.600 --> 22:19.480
And you?

22:20.160 --> 22:22.520
Were you shaken that night?

22:23.400 --> 22:25.600
If it lingers in your heart, speak it.

22:25.680 --> 22:27.000
Do not let fear fester.

22:27.080 --> 22:29.760
Shaken? I've seen far worse.

22:29.840 --> 22:32.040
You think a thug with a stick
can frighten me into an early grave?

22:33.920 --> 22:35.640
Your husband, though…

22:35.720 --> 22:37.040
That night, he was terrifying.

22:37.720 --> 22:39.120
He is not usually like that.

22:40.040 --> 22:41.880
He just cannot bear anyone hurting me.

22:42.480 --> 22:43.920
Yes, yes.

22:44.000 --> 22:46.960
Devoted husband and wife.
Enough to make people jealous.

22:47.040 --> 22:48.040
I almost forgot.

22:48.120 --> 22:49.280
Take these.

22:49.360 --> 22:50.640
These days are unsettled.

22:50.720 --> 22:52.480
We must learn to protect ourselves.

22:57.880 --> 22:59.600
What… What is it?

22:59.680 --> 23:00.920
Cornus water.

23:01.800 --> 23:03.320
I used larger bottles this time.

23:03.400 --> 23:05.080
It ran dry the other night.

23:05.160 --> 23:06.400
Now you will not be short.

23:06.480 --> 23:09.560
Get it in their eyes,
and they'll be blind three days straight.

23:10.520 --> 23:11.760
Cornus can do that?

23:13.560 --> 23:15.880
So that was what you used on Guo Dali.

23:17.280 --> 23:18.480
By that logic,

23:19.160 --> 23:22.280
garlic, ginger, and peppercorns
could all work the same.

23:25.600 --> 23:27.160
Too bad Guo Dali got off lightly.

23:42.160 --> 23:43.000
Headmaster?

23:48.480 --> 23:49.760
Something came back to me.

23:50.520 --> 23:53.320
Once, in the rain pavilion,
we played Go without ever meeting.

23:53.920 --> 23:55.720
Move after move.
Breaking and rebuilding the game.

23:58.320 --> 24:00.160
Who has been playing here?

24:00.920 --> 24:03.360
It seems the game isn't over yet.

24:10.880 --> 24:11.960
I'll play here.

24:13.800 --> 24:14.640
Is that so?

24:16.040 --> 24:17.600
Then it was truly a meeting of minds.

24:21.000 --> 24:21.960
White has played!

24:23.360 --> 24:24.200
Look.

24:26.720 --> 24:29.400
Your Highness, someone
may be inviting you into the game.

24:30.680 --> 24:32.400
Perhaps I intruded upon another's board.

24:36.120 --> 24:38.600
I too have a friend.
An exceptional player.

24:39.760 --> 24:40.600
Yet

24:41.440 --> 24:42.640
we have never met.

24:44.000 --> 24:45.080
How curious.

24:45.160 --> 24:46.880
Go reveals a gentleman's heart.

24:47.720 --> 24:49.240
Though I never saw the other person,

24:50.200 --> 24:52.840
I could glimpse their mind
through the game.

24:53.440 --> 24:55.720
Playing without meeting
is like holding a conversation.

24:56.880 --> 24:59.440
It seeks only that moment
of silent understanding.

25:22.520 --> 25:25.560
Then how do I compare
to this unseen friend?

25:28.880 --> 25:32.680
Though we have never met,

25:33.480 --> 25:35.080
your skill surpasses hers.

25:37.920 --> 25:40.000
Once I obtain your copy
of Hidden Principles of Qi,

25:40.600 --> 25:42.720
my play will rise again.

25:46.000 --> 25:46.840
Perhaps

25:48.240 --> 25:49.640
I shall meet him very soon.

25:53.240 --> 25:55.720
Very well. When that day comes,

25:56.560 --> 25:58.800
we must play a proper game.

26:00.200 --> 26:01.360
Mr. An.

26:01.440 --> 26:03.520
Mr. An, someone has arrived from home.

26:05.160 --> 26:06.000
From home?

26:14.280 --> 26:15.520
Your Highness.

26:18.280 --> 26:22.400
I have come by order to escort
Your Highness back to the palace.

26:50.280 --> 26:51.360
VIRTUE THROUGH LEARNING

26:51.440 --> 26:53.920
The Empress Dowager somehow learned

26:54.000 --> 26:55.840
that you exchanged identities with Mr. An

26:56.440 --> 26:58.160
and came to Luyuan Academy to study.

26:58.240 --> 26:59.480
What did she say?

27:00.960 --> 27:03.760
Mr. An has been confined
on Her Highness's orders.

27:04.360 --> 27:06.920
Her Highness was deeply angered by this.

27:07.000 --> 27:09.880
Your return to the capital
was set for next month.

27:09.960 --> 27:12.360
It's been moved up.
You leave for the palace today.

27:15.240 --> 27:17.040
Your Highness.

27:17.120 --> 27:19.880
I have ordered the rear garden sealed.

27:20.480 --> 27:23.360
No one will detect your departure.

27:23.960 --> 27:28.680
The academy will simply announce
that An Xu withdrew for personal reasons.

27:28.760 --> 27:30.760
All faces remain intact.

27:31.800 --> 27:33.440
You have handled it with care, Nanny.

27:34.800 --> 27:36.280
I only do my duty.

27:36.360 --> 27:39.200
Your Highness, please.

27:45.720 --> 27:46.800
Abbot,

27:47.720 --> 27:48.880
was it you

27:49.640 --> 27:51.320
who played Go with me these past weeks?

27:52.200 --> 27:53.960
I did not expect

27:54.040 --> 27:55.920
that my unseen opponent

27:56.000 --> 27:58.160
would be a young lady.

28:02.240 --> 28:03.600
Of course.

28:04.440 --> 28:08.280
Only the monks reside daily
at Guangling Temple.

28:10.080 --> 28:11.560
I imagined too much.

28:17.960 --> 28:21.000
To play across distance in that pavilion,

28:21.080 --> 28:23.880
perhaps there is fate
binding the two of you.

28:23.960 --> 28:27.560
Why sever that connection, Mr. Gongsun?

28:28.560 --> 28:30.360
I am but a wandering scholar,

28:30.440 --> 28:31.840
with nothing to my name.

28:32.440 --> 28:33.800
How dare I entangle a young lady.

28:36.280 --> 28:38.880
It was one thing
when I didn't know she was a woman.

28:39.480 --> 28:41.160
Now that I know,

28:41.240 --> 28:42.560
it would be improper to continue.

28:45.840 --> 28:47.440
Something came back to me.

28:47.520 --> 28:50.840
Once, in the rain pavilion,
we played Go without ever meeting.

28:51.800 --> 28:54.000
Move after move.
Breaking and rebuilding the game.

28:59.560 --> 29:02.120
I too have a friend.
An exceptional player.

29:03.320 --> 29:05.920
Yet we have never met.

29:06.480 --> 29:07.440
How curious.

29:08.920 --> 29:10.080
Perhaps

29:10.840 --> 29:12.400
I shall meet him very soon.

29:22.960 --> 29:23.800
Your move.

29:51.800 --> 29:54.000
Do you know why I came back?

30:04.720 --> 30:06.200
The road ahead is long.

30:06.280 --> 30:09.320
I only wish that Your Highness
returns safely to the capital.

30:13.680 --> 30:15.280
You knew who I was.

30:17.040 --> 30:19.320
I learned it only days ago.

30:21.880 --> 30:23.320
But when you first arrived,

30:24.360 --> 30:26.560
I already knew you were a woman.

30:27.640 --> 30:28.720
Who is An Xu?

30:29.640 --> 30:31.840
-An Xu.
-He's calling you.

30:32.680 --> 30:34.040
An Xu, my student.

30:34.680 --> 30:36.800
Such striking features.

30:37.400 --> 30:38.760
Such bearing.

30:39.440 --> 30:41.280
Such composure.

30:42.440 --> 30:43.760
I did not expect

30:44.760 --> 30:46.120
you to be the Grand Princess.

30:51.200 --> 30:52.960
I came to this academy for someone!

31:11.160 --> 31:14.120
Your Highness's favor brings great honor

31:14.200 --> 31:16.320
to the entire academy.

31:22.920 --> 31:26.640
This is the copy
of Hidden Principles of Qi

31:27.880 --> 31:29.040
I promised to transcribe.

31:31.080 --> 31:32.960
Please accept it

31:34.200 --> 31:35.280
as a parting gift.

32:25.240 --> 32:27.080
Headmaster. Headmaster.

32:30.760 --> 32:33.000
It is so late. Why have you not turned in?

32:34.440 --> 32:36.800
An Xu asked me to pass this to you.

32:57.520 --> 32:58.680
So it was her.

33:06.080 --> 33:07.240
This match of Go…

33:09.760 --> 33:11.880
I did not merely lose.
I was utterly defeated.

33:24.560 --> 33:27.880
POISE AND REFINEMENT

33:27.960 --> 33:30.080
THE SUTRA OF THE ORIGINAL VOWS
OF KSITIGARBHA BODHISATTVA

33:30.160 --> 33:31.480
Your Highness.

33:32.320 --> 33:35.280
Ever since returning from Hejian,

33:35.360 --> 33:37.440
the Princess has refused
to leave her chambers.

33:38.160 --> 33:40.800
She scarcely touches her meals.

33:41.520 --> 33:46.400
It would seem Gongsun Yin
holds no affection for Her Highness.

33:47.360 --> 33:49.000
If the Princess learns this,

33:49.080 --> 33:51.560
she will be devastated.

33:51.640 --> 33:54.000
Gongsun Yin wrote personally.

33:54.080 --> 33:54.960
His words were sincere.

33:56.640 --> 33:58.880
I admit, that surprised me.

33:58.960 --> 34:02.360
But with the Princess's temperament,

34:02.440 --> 34:04.560
she will not surrender
her heart so easily.

34:10.840 --> 34:12.719
She is still young.
She does not yet understand

34:12.800 --> 34:13.960
the entanglements of court and family.

34:14.040 --> 34:15.040
EMPRESS DOWAGER AN, MOTHER OF QI SHU

34:15.120 --> 34:16.880
The Gongsun name carries prestige,

34:16.960 --> 34:18.440
but they are not a suitable match.

34:19.040 --> 34:20.960
Your Highness speaks truly.

34:21.560 --> 34:24.960
How then shall we persuade the Princess?

34:26.040 --> 34:28.320
Grand Tutor Li enjoys
a sterling reputation at court.

34:29.199 --> 34:31.320
His eldest grandson, Li Huai'an,

34:31.400 --> 34:33.480
has earned merit in the northwest.

34:34.600 --> 34:36.760
I hear he is both capable
and refined in bearing.

34:37.560 --> 34:39.320
He would make a proper match.

34:39.400 --> 34:44.040
Perhaps we should arrange for him
to meet Shu.

34:44.120 --> 34:46.040
I will see to it at once.

34:51.880 --> 34:52.719
Shu,

34:53.719 --> 34:55.280
do not blame me.

34:55.880 --> 34:57.080
You may resent me now,

34:57.160 --> 34:58.680
but one day, you will understand.

35:03.400 --> 35:06.160
XIGU ALLEY

35:06.240 --> 35:07.920
THREE DAYS LATER

35:17.000 --> 35:18.240
An audience with the Grand Princess?

35:18.320 --> 35:22.480
Grandfather must still be determined
to counter Wei Yan.

35:23.360 --> 35:26.280
He likely wishes to secure my footing
among the imperial clan without delay.

35:28.400 --> 35:29.560
In the end,

35:30.960 --> 35:33.600
it is but factional maneuvering.

35:34.600 --> 35:35.600
It does nothing

35:36.280 --> 35:39.280
for the realm's stability
or the people's welfare.

35:42.040 --> 35:43.080
My lord,

35:44.120 --> 35:45.880
the Grand Tutor is your grandfather.

35:45.960 --> 35:47.040
Perhaps you could reason with him.

35:49.440 --> 35:50.720
I may not grasp the intricacies of court,

35:51.640 --> 35:52.920
but at the frontier,

35:53.960 --> 35:55.720
whether it was General He
or Marquis Wu'an…

35:55.800 --> 35:56.840
TO BE OPENED BY ELDEST GRANDSON HUAI'AN

35:56.920 --> 35:58.440
…though aligned with the Wei faction,

35:58.520 --> 36:01.480
they were men who bled
without hesitation for the border.

36:01.560 --> 36:02.720
Grandfather has summoned me.

36:03.360 --> 36:04.600
I must return.

36:06.600 --> 36:07.480
At least

36:08.880 --> 36:10.160
Marquis Wu'an still lives.

36:12.280 --> 36:13.640
As long as he stands,

36:14.400 --> 36:15.680
the northwest will not descend into chaos.

36:23.640 --> 36:25.440
The air is dry.

36:25.520 --> 36:26.520
TOFU

36:26.600 --> 36:29.520
Be aware of fire.

36:37.880 --> 36:39.240
Lin'an truly is a fine place.

36:41.120 --> 36:42.760
If ever the world grew quiet,

36:44.840 --> 36:47.880
I would not mind living
like drifting clouds and idle cranes.

36:50.040 --> 36:52.360
Mother, Sister is here to play!

37:12.360 --> 37:14.360
Has Lord Li truly
gone back to the capital?

37:14.440 --> 37:16.320
I saw him on my way home.

37:16.960 --> 37:19.080
He said the matter
with Guo Dali is settled.

37:19.160 --> 37:20.600
He must report to Lucheng,

37:20.680 --> 37:21.720
then proceed to the capital.

37:32.760 --> 37:33.720
Did he say anything else?

37:34.480 --> 37:36.880
He asked when my parents
first came to Lin'an.

37:36.960 --> 37:38.800
Asked if I remembered
anything from 16 years ago.

37:38.880 --> 37:41.760
I was only 2. How could I recall clearly?

37:42.640 --> 37:44.360
I would need to ask Grandfather.

37:46.840 --> 37:49.160
Changning, roasted chestnuts!

37:49.920 --> 37:52.440
Changyu, Zheng, look who has returned!

37:52.520 --> 37:55.480
BE KIND, DO GOOD

37:55.560 --> 37:57.480
Zheng did not lie.

37:57.560 --> 37:59.200
The falcon truly came back!

38:01.960 --> 38:03.480
You are quite skilled at taming birds.

38:04.520 --> 38:07.040
Or perhaps you fed it too well.

38:07.640 --> 38:09.120
It could not bear to leave.

38:09.720 --> 38:10.760
Is it that greedy?

38:12.640 --> 38:14.160
Since you know the way home,

38:14.240 --> 38:16.880
I will not lock you in a cage anymore.

38:16.960 --> 38:17.920
Fly as you please.

38:31.320 --> 38:32.800
It looks like me.

38:32.880 --> 38:35.000
Was it born of Mother too?

38:35.080 --> 38:36.440
Yes.

38:36.520 --> 38:38.240
You're both such little munchkins.

38:41.480 --> 38:42.320
Here.

38:52.880 --> 38:55.480
The dream beneath
the rain pavilion has ended.

38:57.960 --> 38:59.160
How obscure.

39:04.560 --> 39:07.400
Marquis, Li Huai'an
has indeed left Lin'an.

39:08.120 --> 39:10.560
Mr. Gongsun's diversion was masterful.

39:12.440 --> 39:15.080
I am curious what method he employed.

39:15.160 --> 39:18.080
One more thing. At the border
of Yanzhou and Chongzhou,

39:18.160 --> 39:19.200
bandits have intercepted military grain.

39:19.800 --> 39:21.080
Wei Xuan is enraged.

39:21.160 --> 39:22.560
He has ordered them
eradicated within ten days.

39:25.280 --> 39:28.880
What bandits would dare
repeatedly plunder official grain?

39:28.960 --> 39:30.920
It must be Prince Changxin
pulling strings.

39:33.280 --> 39:34.640
Wei Xuan is reckless.

39:35.360 --> 39:37.160
He may soon find himself ensnared.

39:38.280 --> 39:41.440
Continue monitoring all intelligence
regarding provisions.

39:42.080 --> 39:43.200
Yes.

39:43.280 --> 39:45.120
Marquis, it grows late. You should rest.

39:45.200 --> 39:46.000
Lest the Marchioness…

39:47.880 --> 39:49.240
grow… suspicious.

39:57.720 --> 40:00.160
My tongue outruns my thoughts.

40:00.240 --> 40:01.400
Spilled what was in my heart.

40:02.080 --> 40:02.920
Let's go.

40:09.440 --> 40:11.360
-Candied hawthorns.
-Come have a look.

40:11.960 --> 40:13.280
This one.

40:17.600 --> 40:20.880
EAT, DRINK, AND BE MERRY

40:23.840 --> 40:26.120
Ms. Yu, Zhao Xun
from Lin'an Grain has reserved

40:26.200 --> 40:28.720
a private room upstairs.
He is hosting a distinguished guest.

40:29.640 --> 40:32.160
They ordered our finest wine and dishes.

40:33.920 --> 40:36.040
Very well. Make the preparations.

40:36.120 --> 40:37.840
-I shall attend to them shortly.
-Understood.

40:44.160 --> 40:45.720
TIANYU ROOM

40:47.200 --> 40:48.520
Mr. Zhao!

40:49.320 --> 40:51.800
Your visit brings great honor

40:51.880 --> 40:53.800
to our humble Yixiang Restaurant.

40:54.400 --> 40:55.240
ZHAO XUN, OWNER OF LIN'AN GRAIN

40:55.320 --> 40:56.880
Ms. Yu, you flatter me.

40:56.960 --> 40:58.200
How fares business today?

40:59.720 --> 41:01.840
Business is going quite well.

41:11.160 --> 41:13.520
And this esteemed guest?

41:14.560 --> 41:17.160
Mr. Qi from the capital.
He deals in grain.

41:18.000 --> 41:19.280
We are discussing trade.

41:19.360 --> 41:20.840
QI MIN

41:21.440 --> 41:23.680
A distinguished guest from afar. I see.

41:24.240 --> 41:26.560
Do the dishes suit your taste?

41:26.640 --> 41:28.720
If you require anything, do not hesitate.

41:30.640 --> 41:31.960
The wine and dishes are excellent.

41:33.600 --> 41:36.280
Especially this Snow-Cleared Broth.

41:37.920 --> 41:40.080
This is our house specialty.

41:41.160 --> 41:43.520
It is my honor to serve
our esteemed guests.

41:44.320 --> 41:46.320
Allow me to raise a cup.

42:18.880 --> 42:20.960
If you need anything further,
please call for me.

42:21.040 --> 42:22.240
Ms. Yu, one moment.

42:23.080 --> 42:24.840
Mr. Qi, you may not know,

42:24.920 --> 42:27.920
I haven't been running a shop
in Lin'an for long,

42:28.480 --> 42:30.880
but Ms. Yu has managed
her establishment for years.

42:30.960 --> 42:32.440
Her connections are extensive.

42:33.040 --> 42:35.080
If you seek partnership,

42:35.760 --> 42:39.080
you'd do well to seek Ms. Yu's guidance.

42:43.280 --> 42:45.800
And what sort of trade
do you have in mind, Mr. Qi?

42:45.880 --> 42:48.080
I know little of grain myself,

42:48.760 --> 42:51.080
but should you wish to collaborate,

42:51.160 --> 42:53.160
I can introduce
several reputable merchants.

42:55.280 --> 42:58.800
You are most seasoned
in the ways of hospitality.

42:59.920 --> 43:02.160
You clearly know many people, Ms. Yu.

43:09.800 --> 43:11.360
Yixiang welcomes guests
from every quarter.

43:11.440 --> 43:12.840
Harmony yields prosperity.

43:12.920 --> 43:16.760
In business,
it never hurts to know more friends.

43:18.120 --> 43:20.240
All in pursuit of trade. Understandable.

43:33.200 --> 43:35.000
Please enjoy yourselves.

43:35.080 --> 43:37.040
I must attend to other guests.

43:37.120 --> 43:38.160
Of course, Ms. Yu.

46:30.640 --> 46:34.240
‎NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
‎IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:34.320 --> 46:35.240
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
